  "remarks": "Tehrik-e Taliban is based in the tribal areas along the Afghanistan/Pakistan\nborder. Formed in 2007, its leader is Maulana Fazlullah (QDi.352). Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2368 (2017) was concluded on 24 November 2020. INTERPOL-UN Security Council Special Notice web link:https://www.interpol.int/en/How-we-work/Notices/View-UN-Notices-Individuals",
